## Project Goal

Demonstrate a typical end-to-end data analytics workflow:

1. Data validation and cleaning using SQL
2. Deriving business metrics (revenue, market share, YoY growth)
3. Analysing performance across models, regions, fuel types, and years
4. Building an interactive dashboard for business-style decision support
